Package: QdRant
Type: Package
Title: R Client for the Qdrant Vector Database API
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Ethan Armstrong
Maintainer: Ethan Armstrong <ethangarmstrong@gmail.com>
Description: A full-featured R client for the Qdrant vector database REST API.
    Provides R6 classes for managing collections, points (vectors + payloads),
    vector search, recommendations, discovery, payload indexes, snapshots, and
    aliases.
